{"tid":2100801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鼠王芬反駁曾國衞：初選本身並沒有問題！","createTime":"2020-07-09T10:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T04:05:31.000Z","uid":7542,"like":111,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"7e77cad9f95984a71cf537cd1f9a1cd062a2aa0b","tid":2100801,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>一個唔識法律嘅人<br />\n要一個扮識少少法律嘅人幫佢言論降火<br />\n好羞家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主派批評，政制及內地事務局局長曾國衞的言論，極其荒謬和不負責任，強調初選無外國和境外組織參與，要求曾國衞拿出證據，以及到立法會接受議員質詢。身兼基本法委員會委員的經民聯梁美芬指出，<strong>問題在於參與初選人士背後的行動綱領，並非初選本身</strong>，問題可能涉及《港區國安法》和《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536814-20200709.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536814-20200709.htm&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=4dd9bdb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536814-20200709.htm&h=8b98357e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536814-20200709.htm</a>"},{"pid":"66e3d555720b75b42215f63789b9f6f9fbd94ad7","tid":2100801,"uid":7542,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">聽到鼠王芬咁講就放心啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw 咩叫操控選舉？唔該每個人睇一睇： <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=0af5fafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"fc2dee469b8b84b6ca3aa1b806bd6287b0265174","tid":2100801,"uid":12628,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":3,