01,"uid":236003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"傻閪曾狗叻唔切咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7aa7bd7e21088889d4af2f7be804c3557e85af","tid":2100801,"uid":250654,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"肯定唔記得民建聯都有初選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【立會選舉】民建聯初選細節曝光 設五區諮詢會 名單4月中揭盅<br />\n<br />\n2020-02-09<br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉9月舉行，在去年區選大敗的民建聯銳意重整旗鼓，該黨中委會上月底通過確立黨內初選機制，由領導層及地區支部以投票、考勤等方式，「普選」黨友代表民建聯出戰地區直選和超級區議會議席。<br />\n<br />\n有關的遴選細節曝光。原來該計劃已於本月3日開始報名，本月18日結束，在經歷包括五區諮詢會等一系列程序後，4月中將誕生「準建港之星」，代表民建聯出戰9月選舉。<br />\nSource: XG01<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4e21c3b2c9e20dd0925a5b988ec4040c86c2e0","tid":2100801,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:24:21.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n立多條你初選就得<br />\n人地就唔得咪解決晒"},{"pid":"6ccbf1015c59a09af3fa21506b2edb763254521b","tid":2100801,"uid":240518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"591c22d8773953dfc156036290d1599bdbcbb2a7","tid":2100801,"uid":62226,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"bde280983fc3d5b99e70ae11af438e00398752ee","tid":2100801,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:29:57.000Z","msg":"傻閪AO<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T10:32:17.000Z","msg":"佢唔係AO上<br />\n人地係入境署出身"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T11:29:41.000Z","msg":"想像唔到佢奶都幾勁先上到呢個位"},{"pid":"64ab2df524c2a583b2e28161702aea532a46b2c9","tid":2100801,"uid":80724,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"30233a6cf16b50806b